class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a =
href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DBreadth-first_search&a=
mp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D3" title=3D"Edit section: Example"><span>edi=
t</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>The lower diagram shows the breadth-first tree obtained by running a BFS=
 on an example graph of <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Germany" t=
itle=3D"Germany">German</a> cities (upper diagram) starting from <i>Frankfu=
rt</i>.
</p>
